	<h1 class="title">2015 年，中国人都从日本买了啥？以及，怎么买？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3926/small/3926.jpg?1421980719" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">费丽婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-26 17:00:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/21318/medium/21318.jpg?1453792183" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


